The evidence with the title 'North Korea's enemy: Israel - Israel National News ' says Apr 20, 2012  ... On sunday april 15 Korea's ruling dynast, Kim Jong-un, gave a speech saying that his “first, second, and third” priorities were to strengthen his country's military. His statement, and North Korea's attempt to launch a long-range missile, are a threat to the world. The country most threatened may well be Israel. 
